title: Nij Altoenae
text:
Nij Altoenae () is a village in <a href="Waadhoeke">Waadhoeke</a> municipality in the province of <a href="Friesland">Friesland</a>, the <a href="Netherlands">Netherlands</a>. It had a population of around 300 in January 2017.
History.
Before 2018, the village was part of <a href="het%20Bildt">het Bildt</a> municipality.
